@startuml
skinparam linetype ortho
actor User
actor Stripe as PSP
rectangle TryOnStyleHub {
  usecase "Mua token" as UC_Tokens_Purchase
}
User --> UC_Tokens_Purchase
UC_Tokens_Purchase --> PSP
note right of UC_Tokens_Purchase
Trigger: Chọn gói token, phương thức thanh toán
Post: 200 trả paymentUrl/clientSecret hoặc cập nhật số dư ngay
Exceptions: 401 Unauthorized; 404 Package not found; 402 Payment failed
end note
@enduml

